HEADWORD: overdress
<hw>o`ver*dress"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To dress or
adorn to excess; to dress too much; to dress too formally for an
informal occasion.</def> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
